I need a ride and I think renting a car would be the perfect way to fulfill my need, like embarking on a little adventure.
Do you know when you'd like to drop it off?
Yes, I'll keep it until Thursday next week.
Can you provide me the starting time of your rental?
I need it at 2 in the afternoon.
Please provide me the date now.
I want a small car starting from the 5th.
Do you have a specific location in mind for the pickup?
Yes, it's Fremont.
You have a delightful selection of available cars. I've found 6 options, including a compact Chevrolet Bolt parked at Fremont BART station from March 5th.
I could use this one. Let me have it.
Please confirm the procedure. I am about to rent a compact car from March 5th at 2 pm till March 7th, located at Fremont BART station.
It's exactly what I want.
I can assure you that you'll have your car since I've booked it for you.
How about looking for an apartment there? My only request is for it to have three bedrooms.
If you drive to 1001 Beethoven Common, you'll find Alborada Apartments. The property has three bedrooms and two bathrooms, surrounded by lush greenery. The monthly rent is $3,900.
I love it already! Bye for now.
Enjoy the rest of your day, and may your new experiences be filled with joy!
